  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel has a passion for gastronomy with an extensive choice and display cooking using quality ingredients. </p>
<p>Breakfast consists of a hot and cold buffet.</p>
<p>There is an extensive buffet dinner with 8 areas of display cooking including meat, fish, wok/vegetable and pizza/pasta. Dinner includes international cuisine and dietary restrictions and allergies can be catered for (please advise when booking)</p>
<p>Soldeu's newest spot is KAO, a Chinese haute cuisine experience, this isn't included but is well worth a visit (pay locally).</p>
<p>A Christmas and New Year gala dinner is included with unlimited Cava and wine with the New Year Festival.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
