<li>Balcony or terrace</li>
<li>Fridge and minibar</li>
<li>Tea and coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Mountain views</li>
<li>Some rooms adapted for wheelchairs, please request</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
